
PERSONAL BIO DATA:

Albert is a charismatic
leader of a small,
vocal minority of the
Vault population that
is considering life on
the outside world.
Dedicated to the role
of a negotiator, he is
often able to
communicate efficiently
between different
parties. His professed
occupation is closest
to what was once known
as a "lawyer." Albert
is often able to
convince others that
his ideas are correct.
